title: Driverless Car Gets Stuck in Wet Concrete in San Francisco
description: Though driverless cars have not been blamed for any serious injuries or crashes in the city, they have been involved in several jarring episodes.

title: YouTube Ads May Have Led to Online Tracking of Children, Research Says
description: YouTube’s advertising practices on kids’ channels could have resulted in companies tracking children across the web, a report said.

title: Can’t Hear the Dialogue in Your Streaming Show? You’re Not Alone.
description: Many of us stream shows and movies with the subtitles on all the time — and not because it’s cool.
